    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface StatisticsContainerIfc
    Interface StatisticsContainerIfc Objects which inherits this type can return runtime statistics. Any object can collect job statistics and implementing this interface guarantees that statistics will be presented in configured way to user who wants to see them. Created: Tue Nov 22 07:07:11 2005
